scenario message msg ShouldPrintWhenPlayerMoves direction FromCavern cavern
put player in cavern @cavern
enter command rest
reject message @msg was printed
enter command @direction
ensure message @msg was printed

scenario message msg should print when player approaches object
put @object in cavern 3
message @msg should print when player moves west from cavern 5
message @msg should print when player moves east from cavern 1
message @msg should print when player moves north from cavern 9
message @msg should print when player moves south from cavern 6
If the player shoots an arrow through a cavern that contains the Wumpus, the wumpus dies, and the game is over.

Expand All | Collapse All
 Included page: <HuntTheWumpus.CrossMap (edit)
Create a convenient map that looks like this:

         [6]
         [7]
   [1][2][3][4][5]
         [8]
         [9]


Make map
start end direction
1 2 E
2 3 E
3 4 E
4 5 E
6 7 S
7 3 S
3 8 S
8 9 S

script
  Shoot towards the East.
put wumpus in cavern 3
put player in cavern 1
set quiver to 5
enter command se
check message You have killed the Wumpus. was printed true
check message Game over. was printed true
check game terminated true
 
  Shoot towards the West.
new game
put wumpus in cavern 3
put player in cavern 5
set quiver to 5
enter command s w
check message You have killed the Wumpus. was printed true
check message Game over. was printed true
check game terminated true
 
  Shoot towards the North.
new game
put wumpus in cavern 3
put player in cavern 9
set quiver to 5
enter command s n
check message You have killed the Wumpus. was printed true
check message Game over. was printed true
check game terminated true
 
  Shoot towards the South.
new game
put wumpus in cavern 3
put player in cavern 6
set quiver to 5
enter command s s
check message You have killed the Wumpus. was printed true
check message Game over. was printed true
check game terminated true
 
  Shoot towards the East, but miss Wumpus..
new game
put wumpus in cavern 6
put player in cavern 1
set quiver to 5
enter command s e
check message You have killed the Wumpus. was printed false
check message Game over. was printed false
check game terminated false
